Path: Calling a Command Defined with 
Content:
[link: /commands/docs/def.md] ``def --env``
See 
[link: custom_commands.md#changing-the-environment-in-a-custom-command] Defining environment from custom commands
 for details.
’Щ@e3fa4f89c3fe1fcfd0b4cbb0edcd01b65c1132556032fb496a0cdb9626ecc5ecЩgTitle: Environment
